Two types of scaling are available in system design
1.  vertical scaling (Increase the CPU and memory of single system)
2. horizontal scaling (Create replica of machine)

 Docker is used to build and create the images.
 Docker is usefull when we required single container for lower environment development.

  Pod is the smallest unit.  inside pod container will create (shared storage resources and network policy).

kubernetes : container orchestration tool
A node is a single computer or server, while a cluster is a group of two or more nodes that work together to provide high availability and handle larger workloads
kubernetes will have master node and worker node(pod)  
  
  
